Package sexpression.stream

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASEInputStreamReader
    The ASEInputStreamReader parses ASExpressions that have been serialized in verbatim form off any input stream.
    ASEWriter
    The ASEWriter can take an ASExpressions and serialize them over an output stream.
    Base64
    Encodes and decodes to and from Base64 notation.
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidVerbatimStreamException
    This exception is thrown by S-Expression parse methods if the verbatim string which is offered for parsing is an invalid format.
